ets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (有拳套情況下)</blockquote><br />\n有 谷實比人打腹<br />\n慣左比人打 預先知比人全力打一拳係咩感覺<br />\n對防禦好好多<br />\n同埋盡量練到係預知嘅情況比人打<br />\n即係唔好比人係視線外一個勾拳轟埋黎<br />\n等身體預先有反應</blockquote><br />\n個頭練唔到防守力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n練到，不過比較偏向頸部<br />\n其實頭骨好硬，無訓練既人出盡力打落去，對方可能都會暈，但你隻手既骨就隨時會碎<br />\n<br />\n所以主要都係攻下巴同頸<br />\n<br />\n頸就係用頭做平板之類，又或者練膊頭、斜方肌咁，谷起舊肌去擋勾拳"},{"pid":"029536dfa7a92e26aef3fec4d47e51959c69bc1e","tid":394971,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:41:19.000Z","msg":"屌，以為你話我鐘佢一拳佢會唔會死<br />\n我出返去先<br />\n<br />\n利申：中文u"},{"pid":"9aeab71bf7ecb672e07f4af4fdde416460690551","tid":394971,"uid":100626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:09:18.000Z","msg":"胡師傅呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166acb8aa7f59efdd1301713c9069fb443b2f2f3","tid":394971,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:11:03.000Z","msg":"死"},{"pid":"bb6706aab9521d4f0d36546936c137fd9e82941f","tid":394971,"uid":14878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:15:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">WIFI不破</span></span>"},{"pid":"703adaf3579fcfc9f3faae149d5c487920494299","tid":394971,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中一拳死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拳賽場場死人啦</blockquote><br />\n你攞自己同重量級職業拳手比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜都唔講，你幾磅先？"},{"pid":"afff75818c1b5d2538e4a43e394987c5263c99d3","tid":394971,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:28:06.000Z","msg":"唔洗泰臣 比D普通拳手打中一拳都分分鍾死"},{"pid":"8eb99d5a6f3842c60a6747be670c2d5ed4891a99","tid":394971,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:36:37.000Z","msg":"<b